pesquisaveis.valor: (select b.codigo from bairro b                  inner join LOGRADOUROBAIRRO lb on lb.BAIRRO_ID = b.id                  inner join face on face.LOGRADOUROBAIRRO_ID = lb.id                  inner join testada t on t.FACE_ID = face.id and coalesce(t.PRINCIPAL, 1) = 1            where t.LOTE_ID = l.ID and rownum =1 )

(select b.DESCRICAO         from bairro b                  inner join LOGRADOUROBAIRRO lb on lb.BAIRRO_ID = b.id                  inner join face on face.LOGRADOUROBAIRRO_ID = lb.id                  inner join testada t on t.FACE_ID = face.id and coalesce(t.PRINCIPAL, 1) = 1            where t.LOTE_ID = l.ID and rownum =1 )

(select tl.DESCRICAO         from bairro b                  inner join LOGRADOUROBAIRRO lb on lb.BAIRRO_ID = b.id                  inner join face on face.LOGRADOUROBAIRRO_ID = lb.id                  inner join testada t on t.FACE_ID = face.id and coalesce(t.PRINCIPAL, 1) = 1                  inner join logradouro logr on lb.logradouro_id = logr.id                  inner join tipologradouro tl on logr.tipologradouro_id = tl.id         where t.LOTE_ID = l.ID and rownum =1 )

(select logr.NOME         from bairro b                  inner join LOGRADOUROBAIRRO lb on lb.BAIRRO_ID = b.id                  inner join face on face.LOGRADOUROBAIRRO_ID = lb.id                  inner join testada t on t.FACE_ID = face.id and coalesce(t.PRINCIPAL, 1) = 1                  inner join logradouro logr on lb.logradouro_id = logr.id                  inner join tipologradouro tl on logr.tipologradouro_id = tl.id         where t.LOTE_ID = l.ID and rownum =1 )

ci.ID in (select prop.IMOVEL_ID                 from propriedade prop                          left join pessoafisica pf on prop.pessoa_id = pf.id                          left join pessoajuridica pj on prop.pessoa_id = pj.id                 where prop.imovel_id = ci.id                   and trunc(sysdate) between trunc(coalesce(prop.iniciovigencia, trunc(sysdate))) and trunc(coalesce(prop.finalvigencia, trunc(sysdate)))                   and lower(coalesce(pf.NOME, pj.RAZAOSOCIAL)) ${OPERADOR} ${VALOR_DIGITADO})

ci.ID in (select prop.IMOVEL_ID                 from propriedade prop                          left join pessoafisica pf on prop.pessoa_id = pf.id                          left join pessoajuridica pj on prop.pessoa_id = pj.id                 where prop.imovel_id = ci.id                   and trunc(sysdate) between trunc(coalesce(prop.iniciovigencia, trunc(sysdate))) and trunc(coalesce(prop.finalvigencia, trunc(sysdate)))                   and coalesce(pf.CPF, pj.CNPJ) ${OPERADOR} ${VALOR_DIGITADO})

ci.ID in (select COMP.CADASTROIMOBILIARIO_ID                 from compromissario comp                          left join pessoafisica pf on comp.compromissario_id = pf.id                          left join pessoajuridica pj on comp.compromissario_id = pj.id                 where comp.cadastroimobiliario_id = ci.id                   and trunc(sysdate) between trunc(coalesce(comp.iniciovigencia, trunc(sysdate))) and trunc(coalesce(comp.fimvigencia, trunc(sysdate)))                   AND lower(coalesce(pf.nome, pj.razaosocial)) ${OPERADOR} ${VALOR_DIGITADO})

ci.ID in (select COMP.CADASTROIMOBILIARIO_ID                 from compromissario comp                          left join pessoafisica pf on comp.compromissario_id = pf.id                          left join pessoajuridica pj on comp.compromissario_id = pj.id                 where comp.cadastroimobiliario_id = ci.id                   and trunc(sysdate) between trunc(coalesce(comp.iniciovigencia, trunc(sysdate))) and trunc(coalesce(comp.fimvigencia, trunc(sysdate)))                   AND coalesce(pf.CPF, pj.RAZAOSOCIAL) ${OPERADOR} ${VALOR_DIGITADO})
(select listagg(c.codigo) within group (order by c.CODIGO) from CONSTRUCAO c where coalesce(c.CANCELADA,0) = 0 and c.IMOVEL_ID = ci.id) ${OPERADOR} ${VALOR_DIGITADO}
(select listagg(c.numeroalvara, '; ') within group (order by c.CODIGO) from CONSTRUCAO c where coalesce(c.CANCELADA,0) = 0 and c.IMOVEL_ID = ci.id)

pesquisaveis.valorOrdenacao: (select ev.valor from eventocalculobci ev inner join eventoconfiguradobci evconfig on evconfig.id = ev.eventocalculo_id inner join eventocalculo calc on evconfig.eventocalculo_id = calc.id where ev.cadastroimobiliario_id = ci.id and rownum = 1 and calc.identificacao = 'valorM2Terreno')
pesquisaveis.valor: (select ev.valor from eventocalculobci ev inner join eventoconfiguradobci evconfig on evconfig.id = ev.eventocalculo_id inner join eventocalculo calc on evconfig.eventocalculo_id = calc.id where ev.cadastroimobiliario_id = ci.id and rownum = 1 and calc.identificacao = 'valorM2Terreno') ${OPERADOR} ${VALOR_DIGITADO}

from:
from cadastroimobiliario ci
inner join lote l on ci.lote_id = l.id
inner join quadra q on l.quadra_id = q.id
inner join setor s on l.setor_id = s.id

tabelaveis.valorOrdenacao: (select coalesce(pf.nome, pj.razaosocial) || ' (' || formatacpfcnpj(coalesce(pf.cpf, pj.CNPJ)) || ')'         from propriedade prop                  left join pessoafisica pf on prop.pessoa_id = pf.id                  left join pessoajuridica pj on prop.pessoa_id = pj.id         where prop.imovel_id = ci.id           and trunc(sysdate) between trunc(coalesce(prop.iniciovigencia, trunc(sysdate))) and trunc(coalesce(prop.finalvigencia, trunc(sysdate)))         order by coalesce(pf.NOME, pj.RAZAOSOCIAL) fetch first 1 rows only)
tabelaveis.valor: (select coalesce(pf.nome, pj.razaosocial) || ' (' || formatacpfcnpj(coalesce(pf.cpf, pj.CNPJ)) || ')'         from propriedade prop                  left join pessoafisica pf on prop.pessoa_id = pf.id                  left join pessoajuridica pj on prop.pessoa_id = pj.id         where prop.imovel_id = ci.id           and trunc(sysdate) between trunc(coalesce(prop.iniciovigencia, trunc(sysdate))) and trunc(coalesce(prop.finalvigencia, trunc(sysdate)))         order by coalesce(pf.NOME, pj.RAZAOSOCIAL) fetch first 1 rows only)
